OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWednesday generally dry and
OL,6,Fbright, with some sunny spells likely
OL,7,Facross the region. Light winds
OL,8,Ffreshening a little in the afternoon.
OL,9,FFeeling warm by afternoon, with
OL,10,Fhighest temperatures in the southeast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying mostly dry and mild
OL,13,Fovernight with variable amounts of
OL,14,Fcloud and some clearer spells. Chance
OL,15,Fof patchy light rain across some
OL,16,Fnorthern areas after midnight. Winds
OL,17,Ffreshening a little.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
